projects.description:
Excited to share Aurora, a search engine project built from the ground up with robust features for modern web search. Aurora leverages a powerful web crawler, an efficient indexing system, and a sophisticated ranking algorithm, including PageRank, to deliver fast and accurate search results.

Key Features:
Web Crawler: Gathers web documents, respects robots.txt, avoids duplicate visits, and handles multithreading.
Indexer: Efficiently indexes documents for fast retrieval and supports incremental updates.
Query Processor: Handles complex queries with features like stemming and phrase search.
Ranker: Uses relevance and popularity metrics, including tf-idf and PageRank, to order search results.
Web Interface: User-friendly with query handling, snippet display, and pagination.
API: Provides endpoints for ranking and search functionalities.
Built with: Java, Spring Boot, ReactJS, MongoDB.
projects.title: Aurora Search Engine
